| physical_plan | BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
|               |   SchemaCastScanExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |     VirtualExecutionPlan name=spice.ai compute_context=url=https://flight.spiceai.io,username=,org=spiceai,app=tpch sql=SELECT tpch.tpch.supplier.s_acctbal, tpch.tpch.supplier.s_name, tpch.tpch.nation.n_name, tpch.tpch."part".p_partkey, tpch.tpch."part".p_mfgr, tpch.tpch.supplier.s_address, tpch.tpch.supplier.s_phone, tpch.tpch.supplier.s_comment FROM tpch.tpch."part" JOIN tpch.tpch.supplier ON (tpch.tpch."part".p_type LIKE '%BRASS' AND (tpch.tpch."part".p_size = 15)) JOIN tpch.tpch.partsupp ON (((tpch.tpch."part".p_partkey = tpch.tpch.partsupp.ps_partkey) AND (tpch.tpch.supplier.s_suppkey = tpch.tpch.partsupp.ps_suppkey)) AND (tpch.tpch.partsupp.ps_supplycost = (SELECT min(tpch.tpch.partsupp.ps_supplycost) FROM tpch.tpch.partsupp JOIN tpch.tpch.supplier ON true JOIN tpch.tpch.nation ON true JOIN tpch.tpch.region ON true WHERE (((((tpch.tpch."part".p_partkey = tpch.tpch.partsupp.ps_partkey) AND (tpch.tpch.supplier.s_suppkey = tpch.tpch.partsupp.ps_suppkey)) AND (tpch.tpch.supplier.s_nationkey = tpch.tpch.nation.n_nationkey)) AND (tpch.tpch.nation.n_regionkey = tpch.tpch.region.r_regionkey)) AND (tpch.tpch.region.r_name = 'EUROPE'))))) JOIN tpch.tpch.nation ON (tpch.tpch.supplier.s_nationkey = tpch.tpch.nation.n_nationkey) JOIN tpch.tpch.region ON ((tpch.tpch.nation.n_regionkey = tpch.tpch.region.r_regionkey) AND (tpch.tpch.region.r_name = 'EUROPE')) ORDER BY tpch.tpch.supplier.s_acctbal DESC NULLS FIRST, tpch.tpch.nation.n_name ASC NULLS LAST, tpch.tpch.supplier.s_name ASC NULLS LAST, tpch.tpch."part".p_partkey ASC NULLS LAST rewritten_sql=SELECT "spice"."tpch"."supplier"."s_acctbal", "spice"."tpch"."supplier"."s_name", "spice"."tpch"."nation"."n_name", "spice"."tpch"."part"."p_partkey", "spice"."tpch"."part"."p_mfgr", "spice"."tpch"."supplier"."s_address", "spice"."tpch"."supplier"."s_phone", "spice"."tpch"."supplier"."s_comment" FROM "spice"."tpch"."part" JOIN "spice"."tpch"."supplier" ON ("spice"."tpch"."part"."p_type" LIKE '%BRASS' AND ("spice"."tpch"."part"."p_size" = 15)) JOIN "spice"."tpch"."partsupp" ON ((("spice"."tpch"."part"."p_partkey" = "spice"."tpch"."partsupp"."ps_partkey") AND ("spice"."tpch"."supplier"."s_suppkey" = "spice"."tpch"."partsupp"."ps_suppkey")) AND ("spice"."tpch"."partsupp"."ps_supplycost" = (SELECT min("spice"."tpch"."partsupp"."ps_supplycost") FROM "spice"."tpch"."partsupp" JOIN "spice"."tpch"."supplier" ON true JOIN "spice"."tpch"."nation" ON true JOIN "spice"."tpch"."region" ON true WHERE ((((("spice"."tpch"."part"."p_partkey" = "spice"."tpch"."partsupp"."ps_partkey") AND ("spice"."tpch"."supplier"."s_suppkey" = "spice"."tpch"."partsupp"."ps_suppkey")) AND ("spice"."tpch"."supplier"."s_nationkey" = "spice"."tpch"."nation"."n_nationkey")) AND ("spice"."tpch"."nation"."n_regionkey" = "spice"."tpch"."region"."r_regionkey")) AND ("spice"."tpch"."region"."r_name" = 'EUROPE'))))) JOIN "spice"."tpch"."nation" ON ("spice"."tpch"."supplier"."s_nationkey" = "spice"."tpch"."nation"."n_nationkey") JOIN "spice"."tpch"."region" ON (("spice"."tpch"."nation"."n_regionkey" = "spice"."tpch"."region"."r_regionkey") AND ("spice"."tpch"."region"."r_name" = 'EUROPE')) ORDER BY "spice"."tpch"."supplier"."s_acctbal" DESC NULLS FIRST, "spice"."tpch"."nation"."n_name" ASC NULLS LAST, "spice"."tpch"."supplier"."s_name" ASC NULLS LAST, "spice"."tpch"."part"."p_partkey" ASC NULLS LAST |
